'''Rwooks''' were the most common [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiee]] subspecies, native to the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Kashyyyk/Legends|Kashyyyk]]. They largely inhabited the [[Tree/Legends|tree]]-[[City/Legends|city]] [[Rwookrrorro/Legends|Rwookrrorro]]. Rwooks were distinguished by their fur, which commonly had more earth-like tones than [[Albino/Legends|albino]] Wookiees, such as red, brown, or chestnut. [[Chewbacca/Legends|Chewbacca]] and [[Ralrracheen]] were notable examples of Rwooks.

